title: Jennifer from Group Therapy gives us the details on breaking off her engagement
description: Jennifer was on Group Therapy Tuesday and said she met a guy on a plane and really connected with him to the point she was questioning her relationship with her fiance.  She told us she was going to call off her wedding so she let's us know how that conversation went with her fiance.
